    • Constructor Detail

      • WagonCARTReader

        public WagonCARTReader(LeafNode.LeafType leafType)
        When creating a WagonCARTReader provide a tree type
        Parameters:
        leafType - ClasificationTree, ExtendedClassificationTree, RegressionTree, or TopLevelTree.

        ClasificationTree → IntArrayLeafNode

        ExtendedClassificationTree → IntAndFloatArrayLeafNode

        RegressionTree → FloatLeafNode

        TopLevelTree → FeatureVectorLeafNode

        StringCART → StringAndFloatLeafNode

    • Method Detail

      • createLeafNode

        protected LeafNode createLeafNode(String line)
        For a line representing a leaf in Wagon format, create a leaf. This method decides which implementation of LeafNode is used, i.e. which data format is appropriate. Lines are of the form ((index1 float1)...(indexN floatN)) 0))
        Parameters:
        line - a line from a wagon cart file, representing a leaf
        Returns:
        a leaf node representing the line.
